 Heresy》时</a>，将这张专辑描述为“来自《Biffy》衍生剧的极其怪异的极端暴力”，并补充道：“在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slayer">Slayer</a>的 Dave Lombardo 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BITCH-FALCON">Bitch Falcon</a>的 Naomi Macleod 的帮助下，让我们踏上狂野的碾核骑行。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-empire-state-bastards-thrashing-new-track-tired-naw-3529100">听一下 Empire State Bastard 的新歌“Tired, Naw?”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
