mage-3529052" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3529052" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Hitman 3&#39; Credit: IO Interactive</figcaption></figure><p> “Every Bond kind of defines a generation and it&#39;s amazing how they kept reinventing themselves over so many years.”</p><p> Details on <em>Project 007</em> have been light on the ground since then, but an interview with Abran in the latest issue of <em>Edge</em> magazine has shed some light on what fans will expect.</p><p> “The few other breadcrumbs we&#39;re able to pick up in the office suggest a tone closer to Daniel Craig than Roger Moore, and perhaps a more scripted experience than <em>Hitman</em> &#39;s freeform jaunts,” explained the magazine (via <a href="https://www.gamesradar.com/upcoming-james-bond-game-project-007-is-being-described-as-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Games Radar</em></a> ).</p><p> “It&#39;s been pitched as &#39;the ultimate spycraft fantasy,&#39; which suggests gadgets – and perhaps a step away from the murderous objectives of Agent 47.” </p><figure id="attachment_3529054" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3529054" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3529054" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3529054" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Hitman 3&#39; Credit: IO Interactive</figcaption></figure><p> This therefore seems to suggest a more modern setting and a tone that is inspired by the anxieties of a globalised world with technology reaching all around citizens and spies.</p><p> Additionally, the phrasing of “ultimate spycraft fantasy” might be interpreted to relate to reacting to and manipulating the surroundings to complete missions.</p><p> Immersive simulations, like the <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/deus-ex">Deus Ex</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dishonored">Dishonored</a></em> and <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/system-shock">System Shock</a></em> series, don&#39;t stress to the player that they should fulfil objectives in a specific way.</p><p> If James Bond in <em>Project 007</em> has access to a wealth of equipment that could lethally or non-lethally eliminate enemies – which is hinted at with “spycraft” – then it sounds like the game experience may be more flexible than the <em>Hitman</em> series has been.</p><p> In other gaming news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-to-roll-out-a-much-anticipated-feature-in-steam-beta-next-week-3528930"><em>Starfield</em> will add Nvidia DLSS support in an undated update</a> , as well as announcing that AMD FSR 3 is on its way too.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/james-bond-game-project-007-said-to-be-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3529009">James Bond game &#39;Project 007&#39; said to be “the ultimate spycraft fantasy”</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
